### Get all settings (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get settings by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/category/general
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get setting by key
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings/site_name
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Upsert setting
PUT {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "site_name",
  "value": "NYDEV Learning",
  "category": "general",
  "isPublic": true
}

### Delete setting (super admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/settings/site_name
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

